caller_intent: Caller was involved in a car accident and intended to file an insurance claim but was uncertain whether to speak directly with Alliance Insurance or their agent.

summary: Caller reported a car accident and intent to file a claim but the conversation was interrupted before the agent could provide guidance or connect them with an agent. The call was too brief to determine if the issue was resolved.
